<p><a href="https://asciinema.org/a/a1qh9lypbe65mj0ivfuoslz2s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="https://asciinema.org/a/a1qh9lypbe65mj0ivfuoslz2s.png" alt="asciicast"><ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<h2 id="breaking-changes-from-v2-to-v3" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#breaking-changes-from-v2-to-v3" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Breaking Changes from v2 to v3</h2>
<ul>
<li>NodeJS 0.12 support dropped.</li>
<li>Switched to named imports.</li>
<li>All &quot;snake_cased&quot; variables and properties are now &quot;camelCased&quot;.
<ul>
<li><code v-pre>ExternalEditor.temp_file</code> is now <code v-pre>ExternalEditor.tempFile</code>.</li>
<li><code v-pre>ExternalEditor.last_exit_status</code> is now <code v-pre>ExternalEditor.lastExitStatus</code>.</li>
<li><code v-pre>Error.original_error</code> is now <code v-pre>Error.originalError</code>.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
